---
import WackyLogo from "./WackyLogo.astro";
---

<section class="intro">
  <WackyLogo size={84} />
  <h1 class="intro-title">
    Everything that <span class="intro-struck">went</span><span
      class="intro-insert">is</span
    ><br />
    wrong with OpenAI.
  </h1>
  <p class="intro-sub">
    One long, cursed conversation: lawsuits, outages, exoduses, chart crimes,
    and "opportunistic and sloppy" decisions — from the Redis bug to whatever
    happened this week.
  </p>
  <p class="intro-disclaimer">
    Satirical headlines, real events, real sources. Judge for yourself.
  </p>

  <div class="starter-grid">
    <a class="starter-chip" href="#event-board-fires-altman">
      <strong>Who runs OpenAI this week?</strong>
      The five-day governance speedrun
    </a>
    <a class="starter-chip" href="#event-gpt4o-bait-and-switch">
      <strong>Where did my 4o go?</strong>
      The biggest bait-and-switch in AI history
    </a>
    <a class="starter-chip" href="#event-sky-voice-scarjo">
      <strong>Why does that voice sound familiar?</strong>
      Scarlett said no. Twice.
    </a>
    <a class="starter-chip" href="#event-pentagon-deal-quitgpt">
      <strong>How do I delete my account?</strong>
      2.5 million people asked the same thing
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
